a gauge of deviations in yields from a fair-value model -- hovering near th=
e highest levels since March 2020.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fed offi=
cials are seemingly well-aware of the risk as the portfolio shrinks. The mi=
nutes from May=E2=80=99s meeting showed that several policy makers =E2=80=
=9Cnoted that the tightening of monetary policy could interact with vulnera=
bilities related to the liquidity of markets for Treasury securities.=E2=80=
=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Layer in the fact that capital requirem=
