uency trading firms, and that they don=E2=80=99t carry much inventory overn=
ight. If some investor is selling stocks one day, then some other investor =
has to buy them:=C2=A0There is not a lot of capacity for stocks to be sold =
to a bank without finding a real buyer, and if there are no buyers then the=
